ARC TASK e3721c99
spatial reasoning puzzle e3721c99
the sea perceives training pairs then applies the rule to the test input

observe spatial_eye.rana
observe arc2_spatial_eye.rana

@filter task_colors
  "black"  "blue"  "red"  "green"  "yellow"  "grey"  "magenta"  "orange"  "cyan"

PERCEPTION arc_task_e3721c99
energy 0.50
phase 0.00
spin 0.50
coherence 0.90
coupling 0.50

COGNITION arc_training_count_2
energy 0.30
phase 0.00
spin 0.50
coherence 0.80

@perceive task_summary
DETECT task_id: e3721c99
DETECT training_pairs: 2
DETECT test_inputs: 2

COGNITION arc_pair_e3721c99_0_black
energy 0.00
phase 0.000
spin 0.50
coherence 0.90
coupling 0.00

@perceive training_pair_0
DETECT background: 0 black
DETECT input_size: 30x30
DETECT output_size: 30x30
DETECT same_size: yes
DETECT colors_present: black blue red green yellow grey

